<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>CMS Concept Landing Page</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@500&family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    /* Reset */
    *, *::before, *::after {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d0f18, #121622);
      color: #c0c7d9;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      user-select: none;
      --neon-blue: #00fff7;
      --neon-pink: #ff00db;
      --neon-cyan: #00e5ff;
      --glow-color: var(--neon-blue);
      padding: 1rem;
    }

    /* Navbar */
    .navbar {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 1200px;
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      background: #121622dd;
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow:
        0 0 40px var(--neon-blue),
        inset 0 0 80px #0008;
      backdrop-filter: saturate(180%) blur(20px);
      user-select: none;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .logo-container {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .logo {
      width: 42px;
      height: 42px;
      background: var(--neon-blue);
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow:
        0 0 15px var(--neon-blue),
        inset 0 0 20px var(--neon-blue);
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }
    .logo-container:hover .logo {
      transform: scale(1.1);
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace;
    }

    .nav-links a {
      color: var(--neon-pink);
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem;
      border-radius: 14px;
      box-shadow:
        0 0 15px var(--neon-pink);
      user-select: none;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      transition: box-shadow 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;
    }
    .nav-links a:hover,
    .nav-links a:focus {
      color: #ff33cc;
      box-shadow:
        0 0 30px #ff33cc,
        0 0 15px #ff33cc;
      outline: none;
    }

    /* Main Hero Section */
    main.hero {
      max-width: 1200px;
      width: 100%;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 3rem 2rem;
      background: #121622dd;
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow:
        0 0 40px var(--neon-blue),
        inset 0 0 80px #0008;
      backdrop-filter: saturate(180%) blur(20px);
      user-select: text;
    }

    .hero-content {
      max-width: 600px;
    }

    .hero-content h1 {
      font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 3.8rem;
      color: var(--neon-cyan);
      text-shadow:
        0 0 20px var(--neon-cyan),
        0 0 40px var(--neon-cyan);
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      user-select: text;
    }
    .hero-content h2 {
      font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace;
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 2.4rem;
      color: var(--neon-pink);
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-shadow:
        0 0 12px var(--neon-pink),
        0 0 20px var(--neon-pink);
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      user-select: text;
    }

    .hero-content p {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      color: #a0a9bb;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      user-select: text;
    }

    .learn-more {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.9rem 2.5rem;
      background: var(--neon-pink);
      color: #121622;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      border-radius: 14px;
      box-shadow:
        0 0 15px var(--neon-pink);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
      user-select: none;
    }
    .learn-more:hover,
    .learn-more:focus {
      background: #ff33cc;
      box-shadow:
        0 0 30px #ff33cc,
        0 0 15px #ff33cc;
      outline: none;
    }

    /* Hero Image */
    .hero-image img {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow:
        0 0 30px var(--neon-blue),
        0 0 50px var(--neon-cyan);
      user-select: none;
      object-fit: contain;
    }

    /* Responsive */
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      main.hero {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .hero-content {
        margin: 0 auto 3rem auto;
      }
      .nav-links {
        gap: 1rem;
      }
    }

  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <nav class="navbar" role="navigation" aria-label="Main Navigation">
    <div class="logo-container" tabindex="0" aria-label="CMS Concept Logo">
      <div class="logo" role="img" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <span class="visually-hidden">CMS Concept</span>
    </div>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="/login">Log In</a>
      <a href="/signup">Sign up</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main class="hero" role="main">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>CMS CONCEPT</h1>
      <h2>Landing Page</h2>
      <p>
        A Contact Management System (CMS) in a college setting is a specialized platform designed to streamline and enhance communication among students, faculty, staff, and other stakeholders.
        By centralizing contact information and interaction histories, a CMS facilitates efficient information sharing, personalized communication, and improved administrative processes.
      </p>
 
    </div>
    <div class="hero-image">
      <img src="/images/1123.png" alt="Illustration representing CMS Concept" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
